column5: ANybody out for walley and pike on the sound?  i was out saturday, left midland, fished waubashene, port severn and victoria harbour tough conditions, managed a handful of perch and my first ever musky about 36"  rain, high winds, cold front resulted in a slow day.  thanks
Hey you might wanna start cleaning up for the wedding, with a mug like that it may take a few days!
i'll be out in the sound June 22nd.  Maybe for some pike before that.
I'll be out this weekend for pike/pickerel.  Wayne, good luck on the lakers!
